  "A homeowner is comparing a 15-year mortgage at 5.8% versus a 30-year mortgage at 6.5% on a $280,000 loan. The 15-year payment is $2,350 and the 30-year payment is $1,770. How much total interest is saved by choosing the 15-year option?": "",
